Building the Model

(model_components <- list())
## list()
# summary(model_components <- AddStaticIntercept(model_components, y = train))
# summary(model_components <- AddLocalLevel(model_components, y = train))
summary(model_components <- AddLocalLinearTrend(model_components, 
                                        y = train))
##      Length Class            Mode
## [1,] 6      LocalLinearTrend list
summary(model_components <- AddSeasonal(model_components, y = train,
                                  nseasons = 12, season.duration = 1))
##      Length Class            Mode
## [1,] 6      LocalLinearTrend list
## [2,] 6      Seasonal         list
# summary(model_components <- AddSeasonal(model_components, y = train, 
#                                   nseasons = 6, season.duration = 1))
summary(model_components <- AddAutoAr(model_components, y=train, lags = 6))
##      Length Class            Mode
## [1,] 6      LocalLinearTrend list
## [2,] 6      Seasonal         list
## [3,] 4      AutoAr           list
# SdPrior(0.001, 100000)
# Define the model using the bsts function with the state specification
model <- bsts(train, model_components, niter=500, prior = SdPrior(0.001, 100000))
## =-=-=-=-= Iteration 0 Mon Aug 14 18:33:08 2023 =-=-=-=-=
## =-=-=-=-= Iteration 50 Mon Aug 14 18:33:08 2023 =-=-=-=-=
## =-=-=-=-= Iteration 100 Mon Aug 14 18:33:09 2023 =-=-=-=-=

## =-=-=-=-= Iteration 350 Mon Aug 14 18:33:09 2023 =-=-=-=-=
## =-=-=-=-= Iteration 400 Mon Aug 14 18:33:09 2023 =-=-=-=-=
## =-=-=-=-= Iteration 450 Mon Aug 14 18:33:09 2023 =-=-=-=-=
burnin <- 100 # Throw away first 100 
tibble(
  date = as.Date(time(train)),
  trend = colMeans(model$state.contributions[-(1:burnin),"trend",]),
  seasonality = colMeans(model$state.contributions[-(1:burnin),"seasonal.12.1",])) %>%
  gather("component", "value", trend, seasonality) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = date, y= value)) + 
    geom_line() + theme_bw() + 
    theme(legend.title = element_blank()) + ylab("") + xlab("") +
    facet_grid(component ~ ., scales="free") + guides(colour=FALSE) +
    theme(axis.text.x=element_text(angle = -90, hjust = 0))

r <- residuals(model)
qqdist(r)

AcfDist(r, lag.max=15)

Forecasting

pred <- predict(model, horizon = 36, burn = burnin, quantiles = c(.05, .95))
plot(pred)
